 
<p>

  Australia's not so environmentalist government <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2023/may/11/albanese-government-approves-first-new-coal-mine-since-taking-power">approved a new coal mine</a>.
<p>
That is playing with fire.  Every new fossil fuel investment acts to
accelerate <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#global%20heating">global heating</a> and increase the chance that we cross a
tipping point that tips the world into disaster.

 